{"tid":1458771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要做返個和平安全既環境出黎！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:05:01.000Z","uid":27578,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"98156af4ca82c32f0d6da041f3ec798f9fff0b5d","tid":1458771,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"我建議依個星期要做既係去機場和平示威<br />\n搞機場 最有效又最少損失！！<br />\n星期六個原定計劃推遲先 改做和你飛 減少衝突<br />\n為818民陣既大遊行儲彈藥<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">內部要解決既問題：<br />\n1.前線有鬼既問題<br />\n2.禁止/阻止大台既出現<br />\n3.不割蓆、不分化、不譴責<br />\n今日為例：如果真係清場叫走個班會屌留個班 <br />\n冇清場留個班又屌走個班<br />\n我地各有各做 唔好互屌 態度語氣好少少 柒左咪認</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">外部要解決既問題：<br />\n1.攬炒巴既登報<br />\n2.煽情文宣 可誇大 唔洗留道德底線 學對家</span>"},{"pid":"348e4e0847abcc8a86e6009d7a61e03db2bf6b7a","tid":1458771,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"0ea69172e10f185d5606cc701f4dd8f6b2c193a2","tid":1458771,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"8c88923575dd93904d2f7ed201717f56e255f662","tid":1458771,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"d62835a3b3a5f00cf475717a7f22d914f27baa35","tid":1458771,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"6aa1442b568c4e899d1021eb0cc10802fac562e0","tid":1458771,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"8d17921ef85a25f08cf9a756d08d2d2a184c057b","tid":1458771,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"d2d3de3306a17a2f7997941ad78a58ee3ebdfee3","tid":1458771,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"e6940a8ad2f22